description: Gets the IP addresses for a specified Resolver endpoint.

parameters.name: ResolverEndpointId
parameters.description: The ID of the Resolver endpoint that you want to get IP addresses for.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: For the first ListResolverEndpointIpAddresses request, omit this value. If the specified Resolver endpoint has more than MaxResults IP addresses, you can submit another ListResolverEndpointIpAddresses request to get the next group of IP addresses. In the next request, specify the value of NextToken from the previous response.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: If the specified endpoint has more than MaxResults IP addresses, you can submit another ListResolverEndpointIpAddresses request to get the next group of IP addresses. In the next request, specify the value of NextToken from the previous response.

nested_items.name: MaxResults
nested_items.description: The value that you specified for MaxResults in the request.

nested_items.name: IpAddresses
nested_items.description: Information about the IP addresses in your VPC that DNS queries originate from (for outbound endpoints) or that you forward DNS queries to (for inbound endpoints).

nested_items.name: IpId
nested_items.description: The ID of one IP address.

nested_items.name: Ip
nested_items.description: One IPv4 address that the Resolver endpoint uses for DNS queries.

nested_items.name: Ipv6
nested_items.description: One IPv6 address that the Resolver endpoint uses for DNS queries.

nested_items.name: Status
nested_items.description: A status code that gives the current status of the request.

nested_items.name: StatusMessage
nested_items.description: A message that provides additional information about the status of the request.

nested_items.name: CreationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the IP address was created, in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).

nested_items.name: ModificationTime
nested_items.description: The date and time that the IP address was last modified, in Unix time format and Coordinated Universal Time (UTC).
